Job Description

Duties and Responsibilities:

Communicates technical information and rational analysis to pavement owners (public and private) for the purpose of asphalt pavement market development;

Provides FPO members with technical assistance;

Facilitates member involvement in FPO through communication of issues between the membership and agencies regarding paving materials, techniques and specifications, environmental regulations, etc.;

Represents the interests of the industry before ODO
